content: I already bought, but can not download on TiVi Sony android 55KDx9500H
Can't copy files from NAS to mobile device: "Task error: Permission denied". The app does have permission to access the storage on my smartphone.
replyContent: With Android's policy change, internal SD access is possible in Android 10 or higher, but external SD card access has been restricted. We are currently developing this feature, so please be patient. If you need a refund, please request it.

content: Doesn't work. Not a synology app
replyContent: It is a 3rd party app that uses the official Synology API. If it doesn't work on your device, please report the symptoms. We found a bug where you cannot log in when the NAS device's certificate is missing or expired. Since v1.6.5 has been modified to ignore the certificate check, please update to the latest version. Thanks.
